<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invoice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #0a0a12;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            color: #e6e6f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px 12px;
        }
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .container {
            background: #1c1c28;
            border: 1px solid rgba(106, 79, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(106, 79, 255, 0.2);
            padding-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .details {
            background: rgba(106, 79, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(106, 79, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .line {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .line strong {
            color: #a2a2b0;
        }
        .total-line {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(106, 79, 255, 0.2);
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #32d1f4;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #a2a2b0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #6a4fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Invoice from <%= companyName %></h2>
            <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for your purchase. Your payment has been processed successfully.</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <div class="line">
                    <strong>Invoice ID:</strong>
                    <span><%= invoiceId %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="line">
                    <strong>Item / Service:</strong>
                    <span><%= item %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="line total-line">
                    <span>Total Amount:</span>
                    <span><%= amount %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions regarding this invoice, please feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>

            <div class="footer">
                © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= companyName %><br />
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>"><%= companyName %></a> · 
                <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>">Support</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
